{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On his way back home, lost in the mountains, Barren encounters an adventurer near a mysterious temple. This is Kai, a young man who set out with his friends in search of an ancient treasure belonging to the Laman, a civilization that coexisted with the people of Kaodi for decades before being exiled long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After an incident inside the temple, only Kai has managed to escape. Now, he asks Barren to rescue his companions\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/Group_95_2_.png?t=1740078746\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/BARRENWALKING.gif?t=1740078746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaodi is a short story about the scars that war leaves on the world and on hearts. After being instrumental in the victory against the Shan Republic, Barren must return home on a path filled with guilt, trauma, self-doubt, friendships and broken loyalties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/Inner.gif?t=1740078746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with a wide range of characters. Each will offer a new perspective on the devastation of war: stories of loss, dignity, forgiveness....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/GIF_COMBATE.gif?t=1740078746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All seasoned with a beautiful low-spec artwork, a mix of traditional pixel-art with 3D modeling techniques and effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/Group_95_2_.png?t=1740078746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3325580?t=1740078746","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3325580?t=1740078746","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/0962fb9340a1a74bf57cccc215baf35c1f75c0f8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740078746","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/0962fb9340a1a74bf57cccc215baf35c1f75c0f8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740078746","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On his way back home, lost in the mountains, Barren encounters an adventurer near a mysterious temple. This is Kai, a young man who set out with his friends in search of an ancient treasure belonging to the Laman, a civilization that coexisted with the people of Kaodi for decades before being exiled long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After an incident inside the temple, only Kai has managed to escape. Now, he asks Barren to rescue his companions\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/Group_95_2_.png?t=1740078746\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/BARRENWALKING.gif?t=1740078746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaodi is a short story about the scars that war leave